        <p data-uuid="a488d69147524f1ca395d62ac47db423">Congress voted to declare war on Japan. Germany then declared war on the United States. Less than 25 years after entering World War I, the United States joined the Allies in another global war. This one would be even more devastating.<br />
        </p>
